vpngate - auto connect and disconnect from servers
==================================================

Prerequistites
--------------
g++
make
wget
openvpn
systemd-resolved (for arch)
<other distro specific dependencies>

Installation
------------
Ensure build prerequistites are installed. Run
  
    make

to produce binaries required for the scripts. The build may require root privileges.

Usage
-----
Run

    ./connect.sh

as root to connect, and 

    ./disconnect

again, as root, to disconnect.
